snippet.title: Cat Girl Without Salad: Amuse-Bouche - Available Now
snippet.description:
April Fool’s! Nah, just kidding! Cat Girl Without Salad: Amuse-Bouche is totally real and available now on Nintendo Switch! Take control of Kebako, a cat-eared intergalactic bounty hunter, and blast everything that moves in this genre-defying action extravaganza that combines classic 2D shoot-'em-up gameplay with a hilarious story and weapons inspired by game genres such as puzzle, sports, platformer, rhythm, and RPG! This funktasmical title is rated E10+! 

https://wayforward.com/catgirlwithoutsalad/
